msgstr ""
"Tool results are written back into the thread, both the in-memory window "
"and disk JSONL, while the workspace cache is updated."

#: ../../agents.rst:240
msgid "结束条件"
msgstr "Termination condition"

#: ../../agents.rst:241
msgid "``done=true`` 时先执行当前工具再结束；``tool_name=\"done\"/\"finish\"`` 立即结束。"
msgstr ""
"When ``done=true``, the current tool is executed first and then the step "
"ends; ``tool_name=\"done\"`` or ``\"finish\"`` ends immediately."

